"“translation is orphan”, because “translation owner” is set to a username"
msgstr "“tərcümə sahibsizdir”, çünki “tərcümə sahibi” üçün ad təyin edilib"

#. This string will be preceded by
#. “Warning: the following criteria have been
#. ignored:”
#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Form/SentencesSearchForm.php#L513
